{"tid":104670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬斐森辭任港大校長　返英出掌愛丁堡大學","createTime":"2017-02-02T09:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T09:38:19.000Z","uid":31181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1fb61627f542e9685b998e62234a691fca192566","tid":104670,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:22:42.000Z","msg":"消息指香港大學校長馬斐森已經辭職。港大發言人回覆《立場新聞》記者查詢，未有證實有關消息，僅稱若有新進展即會對外公布。<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞引述港大校委會主席李國章表示，馬斐森獲聘為愛丁堡大學校長，因此辭去港大職位。<br />\n<br />\n馬斐森來自英國，原出任布里斯托大學醫科及牙科學院院長，2014年4月，就任為香港大學校長至今。馬斐森上任後不久，即爆出佔領運動，馬斐森曾到佔領現場。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n馬非森任內港大爆出多場風波，包括李國章獲任校委會主席，陳文敏不獲任命為副校長以及學生衝擊校委會等。馬斐森的合約，原本 2019 年才完結。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/傳港大校長馬斐森已辭職/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%82%B3%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%90%E6%A3%AE%E5%B7%B2%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%2F&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=af4f5437\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%82%B3%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%90%E6%A3%AE%E5%B7%B2%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%2F&h=131ffab8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/傳港大校長馬斐森已辭職/</a>"},{"pid":"4c8af9322e6e968d0700411a52f7677a31fa8770","tid":104670,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:24:36.000Z","msg":"又有一間大學跌排名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab84d667e0d7501315926e946293fa6d0792fe1","tid":104670,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:36:00.000Z","msg":"下次比大陸人做"},{"pid":"a5aa545d64a3ccee5c30a7b41ec742951e3d86cf","tid":104670,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:36:39.000Z","msg":"馬：頂唔撚順香港"},{"pid":"17f0d01a433e9e0a13c47983f13714528e8d7aa3","tid":104670,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:37:32.000Z","msg":"投共失敗"},{"pid":"723e35113c2066e8da76cb6549ef954de8ce382d","tid":104670,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:38:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馬：頂唔撚順香港</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n辛苦錢唔想搵<br />\n岸狗野唔想理"}]}